name: src/index.js
src/locales.js
src/portfolio.js
Portfolio
description:
A portfolio is the list of funds where the investment
is performed

name: remove
description:
Remove a fund from the portfolio. Stats are
updated automatically

params.name: isin
params.description: ISIN of the fund to remove

name: add
description:
Add a new fund to the portfolio. Stats are
updated automatically

params.name: isin
params.description: ISIN of the fund to add

name: summary
description:
Returns a summary with the stats calculated
for this portfolio

name: src/utils/morningStarRetriever.js
parseListOfFunds
description:
Parse a file result of a search on
MorningStar with the aim of getting
a list of funds with the name and
the URL with the details of it

name: getListOfFunds
description:
Returns an array of objects with the name 
and the URL of each fund

params.description:
Array of filenames. Each file 
corresponds to a search performed on MorningStar

name: retrieveFundData
description: Retrieve the URL indicated in the fund

name: parseFundBody
description: Parse the body of a fund retrieved from MorningStar

return.description:
JSON with name, isin, sectors and  
                   regions; null if an error occurs
